Name: XXZ
About the game: Zombie Apocalypses turned out to be somewhat different from what science fiction authors used to write. Only women can turn into zombies. You are spending your holidays on a tropical island when Day Z comes. Your mission is to lead a group of three people who try to escape to the boat. The fight system is based on “match 3” principle. Stunning zombie girls. /
